Package: scagg
Type: Package
Title: Pseudobulk and Metacell Aggregation for Single-Cell RNA-seq
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-06
Authors@R: person("Ethan", "Fenton",
                  email = "ethanfenton27@gmail.com",
                  role  = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides three aggregation strategies for single-cell RNA-seq
    Seurat objects: (1) true pseudobulk aggregation (one sample per unique
    group combination), (2) metacell creation by target cell size, and (3)
    metacell creation by target metacell count per group. All functions
    accept user-specified grouping and metadata variables and produce a full
    cell-to-metacell traceability table.
